own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f919194632a9649a21924f3bcb0cebaf547eedf","tid":335051,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"畀啲醫院波， 或長波放狗咁 玩下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bb4905f2ed72fa435234569738d6fe3ffce710","tid":335051,"uid":102110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"樓主同隊友無夾過? 踢街波好多呢種人。無full team 自己人夾開好難怪"},{"pid":"06ca7be17a5577e3875bf497eee40706cee5d304","tid":335051,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"成日聽到人叫easy easy"},{"pid":"49c98cced38c82d37eff4e241fa2548c8364119b","tid":335051,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"最憎啲人教人踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccb1de345cfd3111bfa8a20963f2f77e254b09d","tid":335051,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主同隊友無夾過? 踢街波好多呢種人。無full team 自己人夾開好難怪</blockquote><br />\n臨時拉夫都好難怪，真係唔知佢地踢法"},{"pid":"b8c24919095d14e1f7f27ad633f2647fb86f3831","tid":335051,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"一腳射到個波出馬路<br />\n講句sor當無事發生"},{"pid":"41028ee19ddeb0f5147dc7321c1714a84eade125","tid":335051,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畀啲醫院波， 或長波放狗咁 玩下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n踢五人場預過一個好鍾意扭既肥仔，全部波比晒佢扭，五分鐘就無氣叫我上<br />\n心諗:開波"},{"pid":"9de9e7d2a7455df5ce070ff2f3d51b0abeefe40e","tid":335051,"uid":30404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"最撚憎啲人係咁屌人<br />\n屌人唔收腳，頂波又話人long柒佢<br />\n明明人地乜都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲衰過啲籃波友"},{"pid":"eade433eedd1b3b92267e361c5b2cdf90e15fb84","tid":335051,"uid":78165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353ebdb142d251b7e50bd2e2a4fa9b3b31d15e8e","tid":335051,"uid":102110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"好隊友可遇不可求"},{"pid":"e6cf3c70d1d1e92ebe5a5e6adb038188c394514d","tid":335051,"uid":35967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"我剩係會傳波 比人屌過做咩唔射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735ca578e25c459b8a333a9502fc5f7a5ecbd184","tid":335051,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a5e5f0ee8be8d9e1eb0d48417ae79bc3d85797e3","tid":335051,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚憎啲人係咁屌人<br />\n屌人唔收腳，頂波又話人long柒佢<br />\n明明人地乜都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲衰過啲籃波友</blockquote><br />\n我見過有人撞完人係到嗌交，跟住話唔撞得返去玩乒乓波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e34beef1753b1c2d02faa014abded36f2ae7e67","tid":335051,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"通常個人閪又自我中心嗰啲咪會咁，一味向前衝唔現位就屌鳩你唔比波佢，自己拎波就自己死推死去，以為自己好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一類自私撚就踢都唔撚郁，對手喺隔離拎波都唔撚追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過有樣真嘅就係肯打防中/box to box又上又落嘅肯定本身性格唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3223892dfddf802b3507e8acec91956b303468fa","tid":335051,"uid":53278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:38:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主同隊友無夾過? 踢街波好多呢種人。無full team 自己人夾開好難怪</blockquote><br />\n好難約到成隊識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同街外人一隊真係唔知點踢好"},{"pid":"9b07698f83c83f88268348f6ab8d3f86c54e49d7","tid":335051,"uid":53278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>畀啲醫院波， 或長波放狗咁 玩下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n踢五人場預過一個好鍾意扭既肥仔，全部波比晒佢扭，五分鐘就無氣叫我上<br />\n心諗:開波</blockquote><br />\n鐘意扭唔緊要 但都要睇時機架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人拍到實一實/推到死位<br />\n都仲扭真係想打柒佢"},{"pid":"2d0da0c9588debb51b886d5fd1e6a67687402bfe","tid":335051,"uid":88250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畀啲醫院波， 或長波放狗咁 玩下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n踢五人場預過一個好鍾意扭既肥仔，全部波比晒佢扭，五分鐘就無氣叫我上<br />\n心諗:開波</blockquote><br />\n鐘意扭唔緊要 但都要睇時機架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人拍到實一實/推到死位<br />\n都仲扭真係想打柒佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌得既都係死扭，扭到死先傳出黎<br />\n見住明明扭生左又要死去，真係會無心機去走位"},{"pid":"73d9afc9f6c2db21ee3c40d2eebb7c6696d9afb3","tid":335051,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"廢唔勤力又扮球星先最黑人憎啊，嘈但肯跑我都忍"}]}